# MLModelStructure.Pipeline

**Structure**

A struct representing the structure of a Pipeline model..

## Declaration

```swift
struct Pipeline
```

## Accessing the pipeline model

- **subModelNames**: The names of the sub models in the Pipeline.
- **subModels**: The structure of sub models in the Pipeline.

## Model structures

- **MLModelStructure.NeuralNetwork**: A struct representing the structure of a NeuralNetwork model..
- **MLModelStructure.Program**: A struct representing the structure of an ML Program model.
